x10.matrix.sparse

Class SparseMultDenseToDense

  • x10.lang.Object
    • x10.matrix.sparse.SparseMultDenseToDense

  • public class SparseMultDenseToDense
extends x10.lang.Object
    Implementation of sparse multiplies dense operations. Results are stored in dense matrices. If sparse matrix needs to be transposed, use TtoCSC() or TtoCSR() on the sparse matrix first.
